libmysqlstub
============
A dynamic loader for libmysqlclient


Introduction
------------
libmysqlstub is a convenience library which provides an interface to 
libmysqlclient, independent of the version of libmysql.

It uses ltdl to open libmysqlclient.so.

Building libmysqlstub
---------------------

libtoolize
aclocal
automake --add-missing --gnu
autoconf
./configure 
make

Features for the future
-----------------------
Crossplatform support
  * Windows
  * MacOS 

